file_content.text: Stick with me, gorgeous. I'll show you the galaxy, take you places you've only dreamt of.
Keep talking, flyboy. I've heard it all.
Don't believe me? My ship's in the hangar right now. Soon as you get off, I'll show you.
No, I believe you. Like I said, I've heard it before.
Left home, saw the sights... and got ditched on a backwater planet. Now I'm serving drinks. You want something or not?
